            <div type="transcript" id="F44B">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Guest is gold and crimson -</l>
                    <l>An Opal guest, and gray - </l>
                    <l>Of ermine is his doublet - </l>
                    <l>His Capuchin gay - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>He reaches town at nightfall -</l>
                    <l>He stops at every door - </l>
                    <l>Who looks for him at morning - </l>
                    <l>I pray him too - explore </l>
                    <l>The Lark's pure territory - </l>
                    <l>Or the Lapwing's shore!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
